{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">OVERVIEW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dark &amp; Evil is an <strong>Indie</strong>\u00a0<strong>Open World Action RPG</strong> game where players take on the role of a young and inexperienced Dark Lord. Fresh from a humbling defeat at the hands of humanity, the protagonist is fueled by the burning desire to conquer the world and reclaim his rightful throne! Build your army of goblins, orcs and trolls and explore a fantasy world waiting to be dominated!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695800/extras/panorama.gif?t=1728866112\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIGHT!</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel the thrill of battle in our <strong>fast-paced</strong>,\u00a0<strong>deep and satisfying combat system</strong>. Unleash your skills  while customizing your playstyle with a vast array of <strong>weapons, armor, and magic</strong>. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695800/extras/tut-final-enemy.gif?t=1728866112\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>EXPLORE</strong>!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse a vast, beautifully crafted fantasy world, from large meadows to ancient ruins. From <strong>frozen tundras</strong> to <strong>scorching deserts</strong>, this world is filled with mysteries waiting to be uncovered!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695800/extras/a-cavallo-verso-la-citta.gif?t=1728866112\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>RECRUIT!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Dark Lord, recruit and lead an army of fearsome creatures like goblins, orcs, and trolls. Each unit brings unique strengths to your legion, allowing for diverse battle strategies. </p><p cla